0.3-81 (Sep 24, 2024)
 * Function for the evaluation of the multivariate t distribution density has been added.
 * Deprecated declarations of Calloc and Free are not longer used in the package.

0.3-8 (Jan 25, 2023)
 * Several covariance structures have been included for the fitting procedure.
 * C code to obtain certain matrix computations and decompositions is now provided 
   by 'fastmatrix' R package.
 * Clean-ups in C and R code.

0.3 (Oct 11, 2015)
 * Initial release of the MVT on CRAN
